  <li style="margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;margin-left:0pt;line-height:13pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:10pt;color:#333333">La respuesta verdadera</span></li>
  <li style="margin-top:5pt;margin-bottom:5pt;margin-left:0pt;line-height:13pt"><span style="font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:10pt;color:#333333">Adivinanza, es decir si es f</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:10pt;color:#333333">á</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:10pt;color:#333333">c</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:10pt;color:#333333">il responder a la pregunta considerando 
